" syntaxPager.vim
" Highlight syntax in vim for paging.
" See: :help syntax
colorscheme solarized

" Highlight the end of buffer area to indicate the end of a buffer.
"
" This is overridden outside of the paging context, because there line numbers
" already indicate the end of the buffer.
highlight EndOfBuffer ctermfg=8 ctermbg=8

"syntax enable
